Michael Vaughan 
On Darren Gough (4 for 26):  Throughout the tournament he has bowled well and been an invaluable member of the squad

stories.title: Flintoff seals six-wicket victory
stories.summary: Andrew Flintoff thumped a rapid 47 not out to help England complete a six-wicket victory over Zimbabwe at Bristol to book their place in the NatWest Series final
